# scripts/

Utility scripts for project setup, configuration, and automation. Contains Elixir Mix scripts and helpers used during installation and upgrades.

## Files

- `configure_credo.exs` -- Configures `.credo.exs` to load Intent custom checks (BracketAccessOnStruct, DebugArtifacts, HighlanderSuspect, MapGetOnStruct, MissingImplAnnotation, ThickCoordinator); idempotent, safe to run on install and upgrade
